===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Shauntal (Masters)}}
Shauntal forms a [[sync pair]] with {{p|Chandelure}} and {{p|Froslass}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. Shauntal became a playable sync pair since the game's release.

Shauntal has also made notable appearances in the game's main stories, the [[PML arc]], and the [[villain arc]]. 

